Class LevelOne

java.lang.Object
com.example.demo.EventHandler.EventNotifier
com.example.demo.Level.LevelParent
com.example.demo.Level.levels.LevelOne
public class LevelOne extends LevelParent
Represents the first level of the game. This class extends the LevelParent class LevelParent and provides specific behavior, configuration, and functionality for the first level. It manages enemy spawning, game-over conditions, and transitions to the next level.
